r du i k\u00f8en, s\u00e5 havner du i k\u00f8en!", "Han gjentar sin misn\u00f8ye med oppf\u00f8rsel slik den man ser p\u00e5 videoen.", "- Overlat trafikkreguleringa til lensmannen, tordner han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "24bd1617731bcf5e1260ddf08c7bbebd1d3f10e2e84ed7fbcbe7b00bad2f95de"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2014-08-30T13:14:32.513Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "- Overlat trafikkreguleringa til oss, sier politiet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/video/article10068898.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/27854.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e53dca4af6958976fec2ef0b0e192d5e0b81858e.jpg?59831ddf"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Her hindres bilisten i \u00e5 kj\u00f8re forbi k\u00f8en -adressa.no", "- Havner du i k\u00f8en, s\u00e5 havner du i k\u00f8en", "Helt lovlig"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "e53dca4af6958976fec2ef0b0e192d5e0b81858e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["felt", "forbi", "k\u00f8en", "kj\u00f8re forbi k\u00f8en", "kj\u00f8re forbi"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["\u00f8st", "v\u00e6retunnelen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "knut sivertsen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/video/article10068898.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/27854.jpg"}, {"field":